name: Nick Mullens
bio: Husband & Father • Minnesota Vikings • Southern Miss  Birmingham, AL

social_posts.post_text: Honored to represent Disabled American Veterans Charity this year for #MyCauseMyCleats. Creating opportunities and building lives after service is essential. Thank you veterans 🇺🇸
Great group of men. Won The North!!
It didn’t take long to realize Minnesota is a special place. Year 6, SKOL!! ❄️💜🤙🏼
Awesome week at PAO! Quality time with a great group 💜
Testing out @kinvent_biomechanics new products. Great information and highly efficient!
6 years of marriage. So much fun, so many blessings. Would not want it any other way. I love you! Happy Anniversary @haleighhmullens

If you knew my grandpa, you knew he was special. I could only hope to live a life as honorable as his. 89 years, 68 years of marriage. At every practice, tuned in every game, loved life and loved his motorcycles. He truly was the man. RIP papa, you mean so much to me.
Husband & Father • Minnesota Vikings • Southern Miss  Birmingham, AL
